    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1 requirements for MRL 2 Class II devices. The CFD hemolysis model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in the CPB use context as described in the claim and requirement documentation. Decision is Accepted with no outstanding action items.",
